keyword.name: core
keyword.message: Event originating from the fdrespub service

event.message: The service temporarily stopped publishing because of a power event.
The service stopped publishing because the default computer information has been removed. The user has elected to opt out of publishing on this computer.
The service is publishing to the network.
Element %1 could not be published because the maximum number of 20 published elements has been reached. Reduce the number of published elements or remove %1 from publication.

The metadata of element %1 would cause the total published metadata to be more than 32k, which is the maximum allowable size for all published elements. Reduce the number of published elements, remove %1 from publication, or reduce the size of the metadata of element %1.
Element %1 failed to publish. Ensure that both PKEY_PUBSVCS_METADATA and PKEY_PUBSVCS_TYPE are set properly on the function instance and there were no errors adding the function instance.
Error calling function %1. The return value was %2.
The metadata of element %1 is too large. The maximum allowed size is 2048 bytes. Reduce the size of the metadata of element %1.
